Params: {1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory14.png'}
{3: 'Babylonia Gray Raven Lounge'}
{3: 'After clearing the game, the group rests their controllers and sits together to discuss their impressions.'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Liv', 3: "So this is what a game is like, huh... It's a lot more different than what I thought they were.", 4: '1'}

{1: '1', 2: 'Kamui', 3: 'So this is what a beach vacation is like in the Golden Age... I feel like trying it out for real as well! We can play real volleyball on a real beach! And even surf!', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lee', 3: '...Golden Age folks sure have a lot of ways to entertain themselves.', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Liv', 3: 'Yeah... Oh, I just looked up some info on the Golden Age database, and found more info on this game.', 4: '1'}
{3: 'Liv displays her findings on the screen. It looks like a screenshot of the page when the game was about to be launched.'}
{2: 'Game Intro', 3: "Memories O'n～Venus Beach is a VR casual game developed by Kuro Games."}
{2: 'Game Intro', 3: '"Immersive beach vacations with a huge variety of swimsuits is its main draw. Players can enjoy a fantastic vacation with their friends through online co-op..."'}

{2: 'Game Intro', 3: '"Preorder will start soon! Share this post to participate in a lucky draw and stand to win a limited edition of the game, as well as the limited summer edition Shark-speare plushie..."'}
{3: 'Some player comments can be seen below the re-posts.'}

{3: 'Carry2513: Honestly, this is the game I\'m looking forward to the most this year. Being able to see hotties in swimmies is pog but I can\'t be the only one who\'s drawn by the "r i c h" strategies, can I?'}
{3: 'sparklingPeng: Replying to @Carry2513: same'}

{3: "Osibov: The GOTY Costume Design Award nomination brought me here. The cloth physics and rendering are so good I can't stop playing! FeelsBadMan that there's no touch, when is Kuro gonna get touch sensors in our VR? ;)"}

{3: 'ulelkeke: Made with a team of AAA fashion designers AND they have full creative freedom. You basically get a free swimsuit fashion show! I hope they deliver... but the price for the devices is a toll on my minimum wage'}

{3: "shakeit: sooo much fun! spent an entire day trying on swimsuits with my friends!! The special must be Mr. P's design, I can tell at a glance! Oh and I got my bae to play and he can wear girl swimsuits lol buy it for this"}
{3: 'dero7: Replying to @shakeit: pog'}
{3: 'Wurd: Replying to @shakeit: nice'}
{3: 'jo: Replying to @shakeit: damn now where do i find a bf'}
{3: 'Claude: Replying to @shakeit: damn now where do i find a bf'}
{3: 'BoredBored: Replying to @shakeit: damn now where do i find a bf'}
{3: 'EsperaS: Replying to @shakeit: Yeah, but the preorders are basically all gone by day 1! How are you guys so fast?'}

{3: "Wadead: Oh nice the arcade games in the game hall map can actually be played!!! the level of details is nuts!! I heard Shome's private water park is opening soon too. Does this mean I can play the arcade games there too"}

{1: '1', 2: 'Liv', 3: '...According to the available data, the game was only available for a limited pre-order once, and only a very small number of players got the game. Soon after that, the Punishing Virus happened...', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Kamui', 3: 'So this game was never officially released...', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Liv', 3: 'Seemed like a lot of people were really looking forward to it. What a pity...', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Nanami', 3: "Nanami can make it more fun! THEN, it'll be popular again!", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lee', 3: "Why would this type of useless data be so complete? Also, it's difficult enough to get VR cartridges in po-pan. How did you find it?", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Kamui', 3: 'Some other recon teams found it when they were tracking the Ascendants. They found this thing in a very hidden place.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Kamui', 3: 'They thought it was something important, but learning that it really was just a game, I asked for it and they gave it to me.', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lee', 3: "I'm more concerned about the lost information in the two melons... I have a feeling that it's not something we should ignore. Well... no way to verify it now.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Lee', 3: 'This has just been... a strange ride from the start to finish.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'But you looked like you had fun, Lee.', 3: '42'}
{2: 'Lee', 3: "Your visual modules must be glitched... is what I'd like to say, but you don't have them, unfortunately. Otherwise, I'd like to fix them up for you.", 4: '1'}
{2: "You weren't your usual self, Lee.", 3: '44'}
{2: 'Lee', 3: '...You mean playing the game?', 4: '1'}

{2: 'Lee', 3: "Instead of allowing these two to turn Babylonia upside down out of boredom, an activity I can oversee is more within control. I'm just making a choice with the safety of the HQ in mind.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Lee', 3: "And well... I never said that I didn't like getting together with people like this.", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lucia', 3: "Sorry, Kamui, I'm late. Ah, Commandant! Everyone's here...", 4: '1'}
{3: "Lucia, who seems to have finished her personal training, walks into the lounge and is surprised by the liveliness. Her gaze falls to the controller in Kamui's hand."}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lucia', 3: 'You completed your mission?', 4: '1'}
{3: 'You pause for a few seconds, before realizing that Lucia is referring to the in-game mission.'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Kamui', 3: 'All clear! But after clearing the level, we unlocked the Nightmare difficulty level. Lucia, you need to try this!', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lucia', 3: '...Okay, then. I will break the highest score this time.', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Karenina', 3: "Wait! Don't forget about me!", 4: '1'}
{2: 'When did you get here, Karenina?', 3: '61'}
{2: 'Karenina', 3: "I've been behind you from a while ago! How could you ignore me for so long!", 4: '1'}
{2: 'You could have called out to me.', 3: '101'}
{2: 'Karenina', 3: "...Well, I didn't want to disturb your game! I know I hate being disturbed when I'm focused on something!", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Karenina', 3: "Oh right! 1v1 me! I definitely won't lose to you in a game!", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Karenina', 3: 'Let me see how this thing is played first!', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Karenina', 3: "...You can't like, install some explosives on this ball? Just passing it around is completely non-lethal!", 4: '1'}
{2: 'This is beach volleyball, not murder volleyball.', 3: '100'}
{2: 'Karenina', 3: "Whatever! I won't lose anyway!", 4: '1'}
{3: 'Karenina drags Lucia into a duel of balls. Kamui and Nanami are acting as referees, and Liv and Lee are sitting on the sidelines watching.'}
{3: '...Finally. A short break in this never-ending war.'}
{3: 'Everyone here must have similar wishes in their hearts.'}
{3: '——Let this holiday go on, for a little longer.'}
